reviewText:
This is a fun and fluid fighthing combo game. However there are some bad points that might ofset some:

1- Later on a controller is pretty much obligatory;
2- Takes some time to really get going and both the story and the Dialog are weak. The artwork is nice though;
3- The resource to obtain Items and Techniques should not be the same considering you don't really get much money;
4- They could've implemented a leveling system to increase your stats from time to time, which also helps with 3;
5- Depending on how you invest your money you might end up with a Spam Fest (which can quickly become boring) or a highly skill dependant flower petal of death;

I recommend it but do yourself a favor and check some other reviews and TotalBiscuit WTF video.
